       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI68102.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI68102.
      *
      *     Expense Reprt - Inserçăo
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD4804 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3401 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6810.
       COPY COCV6811.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT4804 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT4804'.
           05 CON-COVT3401 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3401'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.

       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-X                 PIC 9(04) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA   PIC X(02).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI68102'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV6810-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6810-ASE               TO COCV6811-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6810-ADE       TO COCV6811-ADE.
      *
      *--- Verifica se o periodo está aberto
      *
           MOVE COCV6810-CANO            TO COCD3401-ZANO
           MOVE COCV6810-CMES            TO COCD3401-ZMES
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CSITUER
               INTO :COCD3401-CSITUER
               FROM COVT3401_PERIODO
            WHERE ZANO     = :COCD3401-ZANO
              AND ZMES     = :COCD3401-ZMES
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3401               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK AND COCD3401-CSITUER = COCK0002-SITU-ABERTO
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-CANO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CPER-INV      TO COCV6811-CANO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-CANO-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV6810-ADE         '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV6810-ADE             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *    MOVE COCV6810-CEMPRESA
      *      TO COCD4804-CEMPRESA
      *    MOVE COCV6810-CFUNCIONARIO
      *      TO COCD4804-CIDEMP
      *
      *    MOVE COCV6810-CANO
      *      TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
      *    MOVE COCV6810-CMES
      *      TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
      *    MOVE CON-01
      *      TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
      *    MOVE CON-SEP
      *      TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
      *    MOVE CON-SEP
      *      TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
      *    MOVE WS-DTMESANO
      *      TO COCD4804-DTMESANO
      *
      *    MOVE COCV6810-SEQ1
      *      TO COCD4804-NSEQ
      *
      *    EXEC SQL
      *          SELECT
      *                CNUMFICH
      *              , CIDEMP
      *              , GNOMEEMP
      *              , DTPROC
      *              , DTMESANO
      *              , GPAIS
      *              , GEMPRESA
      *              , CMOEDPAIS
      *              , CIDDESP
      *              , TIPODESPESA
      *              , MVLR
      *              , DTREG
      *              , CMOED
      *              , MCAMBDIA
      *              , MCAMBCORR
      *              , MCONTRVLR
      *              , CIDCLIENTE
      *              , GCLIENTE
      *              , CIDPROJ
      *              , GPROJ
      *              , GNEGOC
      *              , GOBSERV
      *              , CUSERID
      *              , HTIMEST
      *              , CEMPRESA
      *              , CPAIS
      *              , NSEQ
      *              , CSITU
      *              , GTRAJECTO
      *              , NKMS
      *              , GMOTIVO
      *              , IPAYROLL
      *          INTO
      *                :COCD4804-CNUMFICH
      *              , :COCD4804-CIDEMP
      *              , :COCD4804-GNOMEEMP
      *              , :COCD4804-DTPROC
      *              , :COCD4804-DTMESANO
      *              , :COCD4804-GPAIS
      *              , :COCD4804-GEMPRESA
      *              , :COCD4804-CMOEDPAIS
      *              , :COCD4804-CIDDESP
      *              , :COCD4804-TIPODESPESA
      *              , :COCD4804-MVLR
      *              , :COCD4804-DTREG
      *              , :COCD4804-CMOED
      *              , :COCD4804-MCAMBDIA
      *              , :COCD4804-MCAMBCORR
      *              , :COCD4804-MCONTRVLR
      *              , :COCD4804-CIDCLIENTE
      *              , :COCD4804-GCLIENTE
      *              , :COCD4804-CIDPROJ
      *              , :COCD4804-GPROJ
      *              , :COCD4804-GNEGOC
      *              , :COCD4804-GOBSERV
      *              , :COCD4804-CUSERID
      *              , :COCD4804-HTIMEST
      *              , :COCD4804-CEMPRESA
      *              , :COCD4804-CPAIS
      *              , :COCD4804-NSEQ
      *              , :COCD4804-CSITU
      *              , :COCD4804-GTRAJECTO
      *              , :COCD4804-NKMS
      *              , :COCD4804-GMOTIVO
      *              , :COCD4804-IPAYROLL
      *          FROM COVT4804_EXPENSE
      *          WHERE CEMPRESA = :COCD4804-CEMPRESA
      *          AND   CIDEMP   = :COCD4804-CIDEMP
      *          AND   DTMESANO = :COCD4804-DTMESANO
      *          AND   NSEQ     = :COCD4804-NSEQ
      *    END-EXEC
      *
      *
      *    MOVE CON-COVT4804
      *      TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
      *    PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
      *       THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       IF DB2-OK
      *          IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
      *             MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *               TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *             MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-S
      *             MOVE COCK0001-CFUNCIONARIO-EXISTS
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
      *             MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
      *          ELSE
      *             MOVE COCD4804-CEMPRESA  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA
      *             MOVE COCD4804-CIDEMP    TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO
      *             MOVE COCD4804-DTMESANO  TO COCV6811-DTMESANO
      *             MOVE COCD4804-NSEQ      TO COCV6811-SEQ1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-CIDPROJ   TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-CIDDESP   TO COCV6811-CIDDESP1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-DTREG     TO COCV6811-DTREG1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-MVLR      TO COCV6811-MVLR1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-CMOED     TO COCV6811-CMOED1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-GOBSERV   TO COCV6811-GOBSERV1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-GTRAJECTO TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-NKMS      TO COCV6811-NKMS1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-GMOTIVO   TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO1
      *             MOVE COCD4804-IPAYROLL  TO COCV6811-IPAYROLL1
      *
      *             IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
      *                 CONTINUE
      *             END-IF
      *          END-IF
      *       ELSE
      *          IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
      *             MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *               TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *             MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-S
      *             MOVE COCK0001-CFUNCIONARIO-N-EXISTS
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
      *             MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
      *               TO COCV6811-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
      *          END-IF
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6811-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV6811-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6811-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
